                    Specifies the value whose floating point encoding to return.
                </p></dd></dl></div></div><div class="refsect1"><a id="description"></a><h2>Description</h2><p>
            <code class="function">floatBitsToInt</code> and <code class="function">floatBitsToUint</code> return the encoding
            of their floating-point parameters as <code class="code">int</code> or <code class="code">uint</code>, respectively. The
            floating-point bit-level representation is preserved.
